1 (v) Dogfighting, cockfighting, bearbaiting, or pitting an animal
2 against another under section 28-1005; or
3 (w) Promoting gambling in the first degree under section 28-1102.
4 (2) Unlawful membership recruitment into an organization or
5 association is a Class IV felony.
6 Sec. 7. Original section 28-1204.02, Reissue Revised Statutes of
7 Nebraska, sections 28-1201 and 28-1351, Revised Statutes Cumulative
8 Supplement, 2024, and section 28-101, Revised Statutes Supplement, 2025,
9 are repealed.
